Class User

java.lang.Object
com.cb.backend.model.User
@Entity public class User extends Object
Entity User represents an application user.

This entity is mapped to the CB_USERS table and is used to store authentication and profile information such as username, email, password data, role, profile image, and creation date.

Each user has exactly one Role that defines access level within the application.

Since:
1.0
Author:
Dmytro Babich
